import React from "react";
import {
  Body,
  CardArticle,
  Container,
  ContainerArticle,
  Header,
  Title,
  Thumbnail,
  TitleArticle,
  Description,
  BodyArticle,
  BodyText,
} from "../styled/Home";

export default function HomePage() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Header>
        <Title>CRUD</Title>
      </Header>
      <Body>
        <ContainerArticle>
          <CardArticle>
            <Thumbnail src="http://placehold.it/" />
            <TitleArticle>Title</TitleArticle>
            <Description>Description</Description>
            <BodyArticle>
              <BodyText>body</BodyText>
            </BodyArticle>
          </CardArticle>
        </ContainerArticle>
      </Body>
    </Container>
  );
}
